body:
@quydev I do not see how `tf.image.pad_to_bounding_box` helps here. I did not specify how to do the final padding/cropping, and anyway `pad_to_bounding_box` does that by using `tf.pad` (see [image_ops_impl.py
:646](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/eafd4671772b111b3ed12c4c0b4f355248ecee30/tensorflow/python/ops/image_ops_impl.py#L646).
But the commit looks really promising! Would be nice to see this in the next release :)
